    <p><strong>We don't do:</strong> building circuit work (breaker, wall receptacle, supply wiring 240V) which is electrical contractor scope; new electric cooktop installation (specialty installer trade including high-amp circuit rough-in); induction cooktops on this page (separate equipment category, see <a href="/commercial/stove-repair/induction-cooktop-repair/">induction cooktop repair</a>); commercial range service with oven on this page (see <a href="/commercial/range-repair/">commercial range repair</a> for ranges with ovens).</p>
